                     </tr>
                     <tr>
                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24">(d)</td>
                        <td colspan="4" valign="top" width="264">$20,000,000 is available to the Ocean Protection Council to implement the California Sea Level Rise Mitigation and Adaptation
                           Act of 2021.
                        </td>
                        <td align="right" valign="bottom" width="80"></td>
                     </tr>
                     <tr>
                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24">(e)</td>
                        <td colspan="4" valign="top" width="264">$7,000,000 is available to the Ocean Protection Council to support the restoration and management of kelp ecosystems.</td>
                        <td align="right" valign="bottom" width="80"></td>
                     </tr>
                     <tr>
                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24">(f)</td>
                        <td colspan="4" valign="top" width="264">$5,000,000 is available for a grant to the Wildlife Conservation Board to protect and restore island ecosystems by mitigating
                           the threat of island invasive species and advancing
                           					 biosecurity initiatives.
                        </td>
                        <td align="right" valign="bottom" width="80"></td>
                     </tr>
                     <tr>
                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
