                     <tr>
                        <td width="24"></td>
                        <td colspan="7" valign="top" width="392">Provisions:</td>
                     </tr>
                     <tr>
                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24">1.</td>
                        <td colspan="5" valign="top" width="288">The funds appropriated in this item shall be available for projects in California that provide long-term capital infrastructure
                           to use forest and other vegetative waste removed for wildfire mitigation for noncombustible uses that maximize reductions
                           in greenhouse gas emissions, provide local air quality benefits, and increase local community resilience against climate change
                           impacts.
                        </td>
                        <td align="right" valign="bottom" width="80"></td>
                     </tr>
                     <tr>
                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24">2.</td>
                        <td colspan="5" valign="top" width="288">The funds appropriated in this item shall be available for encumbrance or expenditure until June 30, 2028.</td>
