                        <td align="right" valign="bottom" width="80"></td>
                     </tr>
                     <tr>
                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24">4.</td>
                        <td colspan="5" valign="top" width="288">Of the amount appropriated in this item, $10,003,000 shall be granted to the Department of Fish and Wildlife for migratory
                           bird programs as follows:
