                     </tr>
                     <tr>
                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24">5.</td>
                        <td colspan="5" valign="top" width="288">For the purposes of this item, the Great Redwood Trail shall be defined as a non-motorized trail between the Dividing line,
