                        <td colspan="4" style="keep-together.within-page:always;" valign="top" width="214">
                           <div style="">Reimbursements to 3960022-Benefits (Medical Care and Services)
                              ........................
                              		
                           </div>
                        </td>
                        <td align="right" valign="bottom" width="74">−2,994,825,000</td>
