                           healthcare workforce, and payment rates above and beyond those already in effect or in existence as of January 1, 2024, and
                           are in addition to existing reimbursement rates and any other payments made by the department as of January 1, 2024, and do
                           not supplant amounts that would otherwise be payable by a Medi-Cal managed care plan or the department, as applicable, to
                           a recipient of moneys provided by Article 4 (commencing
                           					 with Section 141900.109) of Chapter 7.5 of Part 3 of Division 9 of the Welfare and Institutions Code.
