                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24">(e)</td>
                        <td colspan="4" valign="top" width="264">Funding spent on services pursuant to subprovision (d) may be used to cover costs associated with Proposition 36 (2024) that
