                           <div style="">Notwithstanding any other law, the allocation of these funds by the State Department of Social Services shall be exempt from
                              the requirements of Article 4 (commencing with Section 19130) of Chapter 5 of Part 2 of Division 5 of Title 2 of the Government
                              Code, and from the Public Contract Code and the State Contracting Manual, and shall not be subject to the review or approval
                              of the Department of General Services.
