                     <tr>
                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24">4.</td>
                        <td colspan="5" valign="top" width="288">
                           <div style="">Notwithstanding any other law, upon selection of the State of California, the Department of Finance may augment this item
                              in Schedule (1) for future annual expenditure authority to expend funding awarded
                              					 through the Preschool Development Grant, no sooner than 30 days after notification in writing is provided to the chairpersons
                              of the fiscal committees in each house of the Legislature and the Chairperson of the Joint Legislative Budget Committee.
                           </div>
                        </td>
                        <td valign="bottom" width="80"></td>
