            <div id="s1920.9869384421769732">
               <div style="margin:0 0 1em 0" class="ActionLine">
                  <h3 style="font-weight:bold; display:inline;"><font color="blue" class="blue_text"><i>SEC. 192.</i></font></h3> <font color="blue" class="blue_text"><i>Item 5180-491 of Section 2.00 of the Budget Act of 2025 is amended to read:</i></font>
               </div>
               <div>
                  <table frame="">
                     <tr>
                        <td colspan="7" valign="top" width="336">
                           <div style="">5180-491—Reappropriation, State Department of Social Services. The amounts specified in the following citations are reappropriated
                              for the purposes provided for in those appropriations and shall be available for encumbrance or expenditure until June 30,
                              2026:
                           </div>
                        </td>
                        <td align="right" valign="bottom" width="80"></td>
                     </tr>
