                              California Technical Assistance Network servers and optimization of search capabilities.
                           </div>
                        </td>
                        <td valign="bottom" width="80"></td>
                     </tr>
                     <tr>
                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24">16.</td>
                        <td colspan="5" valign="top" width="288">
                           <div style="">Of the funds appropriated in Schedule (5), $2,165,000 is available in one-time carryover funds.</div>
                        </td>
                        <td valign="bottom" width="80"></td>
                     </tr>
                  </table>
               </div>
