                           		<style>span.DottedLeaders::after {content:"..................";}</style><font color="#B30000"><s>2.4%</s></font><font color="blue" class="blue_text"><i>0.0%</i></font> of pensionable compensation.
                        </div>
                        <div style="margin:0 0 1em 0;"></div>
